title: Sub Pop gig poster
author: psychictensions

comments.content:
It must be **[Brandon Text (Black)](http://web.archive.org/web/20150317113817/http:/www.findmyfont.com/index.php/fonts/font-preview?fset=HVDFonts%20%2F%20%28Commercial%29&ffam=Brandon%20Text%20-%20Black&fid=9edcb0f3b1b7f0478b7243a4ca9df922&fsize=48&text=HIS%20ELECTRO%20BLUE%20VOICE%20HAVAH%20PRETTY%20HURTS&wrap=2)** by Hannes von Doehren [HVDFonts, 2012]  
 **[Museo Sans Rounded (900)](http://web.archive.org/web/20150317113817/http:/www.findmyfont.com/index.php/fonts/font-preview?fset=Exljbris%20%2F%20%28Commercial%29&ffam=Museo%20Sans%20Rounded%20-%20900&fid=7002ff77f380cfd275865383c91694a3&fsize=48&text=HIS%20ELECTRO%20BLUE%20VOICE%20HAVAH%20PRETTY%20HURTS&wrap=2)** by Jos Buivenga [Exljbris, 2011] is also close but not an exact match.
